The '''Alaskan Mission Operations Center''' ('''AMOC''') is a U.S. [[National Security Agency]] facility located on [[Elmendorf Air Force Base]] in [[Anchorage]], [[Alaska]].<ref name=factsheet>{{cite web |title=U.S. Air Force Fact Sheet: 70th Intelligence, Surveillance and Reconnaissance Wing |publisher=[[U.S. Air Force]] |url=http://www.afisr.af.mil/library/factsheets/factsheet_print.asp?fsID=14145&page=1 |date=March 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130312153309/http://www.afisr.af.mil/library/factsheets/factsheet_print.asp?fsID=14145&page=1 |archivedate=12 March 2013 |accessdate=16 July 2014}}</ref> The facility is considered one of two "consolidated intelligence centers" and is supported by the [[373d Intelligence, Surveillance and Reconnaissance Group]] of the [[70th Intelligence, Surveillance and Reconnaissance Wing]] of the [[U.S. Air Force]].<ref name=factsheet /><ref name=cryptoops>{{cite web |title=Air Force ISR Agency Instruction 10-102: Cryptologic Operations|publisher=[[U.S. Air Force]] |url=http://web.elastic.org/~fche/mirrors/www.jya.com/dodi/AFISRAI10-102.pdf |date=November 14, 2007 |accessdate=July 16, 2014}}</ref> Along with the [[Misawa Security Operations Center]] (MSOC) in [[Japan]], AMOC provides [[Military intelligence|combat intelligence]] to battlefield commanders, [[Command (military formation)|commands]] and [[U.S. Department of Defense]] leadership.<ref name=factsheet /> The NSA operation at Elmendorf AFB was a suspected [[ECHELON]] ground station.<ref name=afp>{{cite news|title=Declassified documents confirm secret worldwide US surveillance network |publisher=[[Yahoo! News]] |agency=[[Agence France-Presse]] |url=http://sg.dailynews.yahoo.com/headlines/technology/afp/article.html?s=singapore/headlines/000204/technology/afp/Declassified_documents_confirm_secret_worldwide_US_surveillance_network.html |date=February 4, 2000 |archiveurl=https://famguardian.org/disks/TaxDVD/Researchers/Meador,Dan/US%20surveillance%20network.doc |archivedate=an unknown date }}{{dead link|date=October 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

